What you need to know:

Substitute Hassan restored Harambee Stars' lead in the 59th minute when he buried a shot in the right corner of the goal post after Juma found him inside the box with a short pass.Harambee Stars introduced Elvis Rupia and Henry Meja for Kimani and Lawrence Juma respectively. On the other hand, Taifa Stars brought in Hamish Suleimani, Mustapha Salumi and John Pius for Mussa Shah, Clement Kibabage and Lyanga respectively.